sketch.compiler.ast.core.stmts

Class StmtIfThen

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENode
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.stmts.Statement
        • sketch.compiler.ast.core.stmts.StmtIfThen

  • public class StmtIfThen
extends Statement
    A standard conditional statement. This has a conditional expression and two optional statements. If the condition is true, the first statement (the consequent) is executed; otherwise, the second statement (the alternative) is executed.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    David Maze <dmaze@cag.lcs.mit.edu>
